tum.dss.thesis.knapsack

Class KnapsackDataGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • tum.dss.thesis.lsframework.AbstractMechanismData
      • tum.dss.thesis.knapsack.KnapsackDataGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, MechanismDataInterface

    public class KnapsackDataGenerator
extends AbstractMechanismData
    Class to generate very simple knapsack data and save it to a file. Files can be read by KnapsackDataReader
    Author:
    Florian Stallmann
    See Also:
